# ============================================================
# REST Client - API Quotes
# Requiere la extension REST Client de Huachao en VS Code
# https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
# ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

# Token de ejemplo
# Para obtener uno nuevo, ejecutar primero auth.http
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6ImFsdW1ubyIsImlhdCI6MTc3ODExMzcwMSwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MTIwOTAxfQ.gkvHf3_aZk_3KeLGBzMFE1bYYN7GDopPCi7V5_0yE60

# Variable para reutilizar el id del favorito creado.
# Completar manualmente con el id devuelto por el POST.
@favoriteId = 1778110078190

### Verificación de estado del servidor (Health Check)
GET http://localhost:3000/health

# ============================================================
# 1. GET /quotes/random
# Espera: 200 { quote, author }
# ============================================================

### Obtener frase aleatoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes/random
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



# ============================================================
# 2. POST /quotes/favorites
# Espera: 201 { message, favorite }
# El favorite debe incluir id y createdAt
# ============================================================

### Agregar frase a favoritos (caso exitoso)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quote": "The only way to do great work is to love what you do.",
  "author": "Steve Jobs"
}

###

### Agregar otra frase para tener mas de un favorito
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quote": "In the middle of difficulty lies opportunity.",
  "author": "Albert Einstein"
}

###

### Error 400 - body sin campo quote
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "author": "Autor sin frase"
}

###

### Error 400 - body sin campo author
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quote": "Una frase sin autor"
}

###

### Error 400 - body completamente vacio
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}


# ============================================================
# 3. GET /quotes/favorites
# Espera: 200 { favorites: [ ... ] }
# ============================================================

### Listar todos los favoritos
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# PRUEBA DE PERSISTENCIA
# Detener el servidor (Ctrl+C), volver a iniciarlo con npm start
# y ejecutar este request de nuevo. Los favoritos deben seguir presentes.
### Verificar persistencia tras reinicio del servidor
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ============================================================
# 4. DELETE /quotes/favorites/:id
# Espera: 200 { message }
# ============================================================

### Eliminar favorito por id (reemplazar @favoriteId antes de ejecutar)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites/{{favoriteId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Error 404 - id que no existe
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/quotes/favorites/99999999999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}